data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to this stunning property with a natural color palette that exudes a calm and soothing ambiance. The heart of the home is the kitchen, equipped with a center island providing ample space for meal preparation and casual dining. The kitchen also boasts a nice backsplash, adding a touch of elegance to the space. In addition to the spacious bedrooms, this home offers other rooms that can be utilized as flexible living areas, accommodating the needs of any homeowner. The primary bathroom features double sinks, allowing for convenience and functionality. Furthermore, the primary bathroom offers good under sink storage, ensuring all of your essentials are neatly organized. With fresh interior paint throughout, this home feels crisp and inviting, ready for you to make it your own. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable property.
